    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In SYNCANITE FOUNDATION, you take on the role of a unique oligarch and plan your coup from the shadows to take over the world. While doing so, you need to eliminate your rivals by using military force in the 1st, asymmetric area control phase; economic means in the 2nd, resource management phase and political pressure in the 3rd phase, in which you pass laws that add new rules and eventually trigger one or multiple crisis. Each of these unlocks a new game mechanic and thus opens a path to victory. Its core version is for 2-4 players and lasts 30-45 mins per player. The expansion is for 1-6 players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133130/extras/58ba77a6b2f7669168533833d7aa38e4.avif?t=1739798691\" width=616 height=1000 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133130/extras/2cb293d6ad9fa38610ff096b8e48ecc8.poster.avif?t=1739798691\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133130/extras/2cb293d6ad9fa38610ff096b8e48ecc8.webm?t=1739798691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133130/extras/2cb293d6ad9fa38610ff096b8e48ecc8.mp4?t=1739798691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133130/extras/e35cd04ed82cd1f82355ab257c2719a3.avif?t=1739798691\" width=680 height=974 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133